chapters.title: Stop Using Phony Science to Justify Transphobia
Tim's Feelings on the Culture Wars

description:
Part 2 of 2.

In finishing this video, I feel like there's so much more to say about Tim Pool, but I don't think I can quite bring myself to cover any of his content for the foreseeable future. A broader look at his work, and his origins, I think would help contextualize this very determined effort he's making to produce some truly awful commentary.


I know my opinion that he's at least partially genuine is at odds with some people who see him as a pure grifter, but I don't know if the degree of ineptitude he displays is something that can be faked. If it's all an act, and he's suckered me, I have to give him total credit for being so utterly convincing as a man completely out of his depth.

I'm writing this description weird. Hopefully it works for someone though!
